sequenceDiagram
    title Order Processing
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant API as API Server
    actor DB as Database

    Client->>API: POST /orders
    activate API
    API->>DB: INSERT order
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: order_id
    deactivate DB

    alt Success
        API-->>Client: 201 Created
    else Validation Error
        API-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
    end

    loop Retry 3 times
        API->>DB: Check status
        DB-->>API: pending
    end

    opt Notification
        API-)Client: WebSocket update
    end

    note over Client,API: Authentication required
    note right of DB: Async replication

    deactivate API
